## Available Functions

This provider offers the following functions:

- [`encode`](functions/encode.md) - Convert Unicode strings to punycode (ASCII-compatible encoding)
- [`decode`](functions/decode.md) - Convert punycode strings back to Unicode

## Use Cases

The Punycode provider is useful for:

- **DNS Configuration**: Converting international domain names to ASCII format for DNS records
- **URL Processing**: Handling internationalized domain names in URLs
- **Domain Registration**: Preparing international domain names for registration systems
- **API Integration**: Working with systems that require ASCII-only domain names

